reviewText: I have been trying to find this movie for a long time,I finally have it. I only wish it could be downloaded and saved for later viewing. Amazon got the movie rentals priced just right.

The usual good guys/bad guys theme with the added touch of a killer who dresses all in white and turns out to be - well - find for yourself. The kung Fu is impressive but familiar and goes on a little too long.
What more can I say. It's an old Chinese kung fu movie.
Dumb, really dumb movie. Lousy quality and even more lousy acting! Time waster.
Poor quality, wasn't quite what I expected according to other reviews.
